市值的這天，大家又似乎已忘記Facebook、Twitter以致騰訊近日的急跌，正反映了被動基金令資產過度集中的風險。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.etf.com/sections/index-investor-corner/swedroe-passive-investing-demonized?nopaging=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etf.com%2Fsections%2Findex-investor-corner%2Fswedroe-passive-investing-demonized%3Fnopaging%3D1&d=0QVthNlhK99TeRNrWxp4kC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=133f831a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.etf.com/sections/index-investor-corner/swedroe-passive-investing-demonized?nopaging=1</a><br />\n又將指數基金妖魔化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"損害佢地利益，當然要唱衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ea3d7b2913e3bd1c4b273771d99126d7bfd416","tid":773990,"uid":129924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"香港收得貴咪一樣借貨比人沽空沽鳩自己d股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到香港d基金淨係收手續費咁"},{"pid":"b5eae264345513fb806a41687706cc32217ec566","tid":773990,"uid":158480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1ea3d7b2913e3bd1c4b273771d99126d7bfd416","tid":773990,"uid":129924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"香港收得貴咪一樣借貨比人沽空沽鳩自己d股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到香港d基金淨係收手續費咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:52:27.000Z","msg":"你做咩講出來姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077455bfe2f695f61b82a49eae7c7e152e6d2aef","tid":773990,"uid":57424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5eae264345513fb806a41687706cc32217ec566","tid":773990,"uid":158480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1ea3d7b2913e3bd1c4b273771d99126d7bfd416","tid":773990,"uid":129924,"like":3,"dislik